{"tid":1638351,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民建聯譴責議員辦事處遭受破壞　 籲與示威者「割席」","createTime":"2019-10-08T09:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T13:20:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0524c01aeaaab20aaedcd54a31b4f3c2d4c70cbe","tid":1638351,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191008/_2019100816112031542.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191008%2F_2019100816112031542.jpeg&h=2aeba462&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191008/_2019100816111984460.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191008%2F_2019100816111984460.jpeg&h=0127de93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日示威活動中，民建聯有4名議員的辦事處遭受破壞及縱火，街站亦受到滋擾，民建聯譴責有關暴力行為，令社區多處受破壞，呼籲民主派與示威者「割席」，回復社會安寧。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯主席李慧琼形容，社會已陷入半癱瘓狀態，不少商店要關門，市民不敢外出，亦沒有交通工具，令到香港內傷，希望市民可以「不違法、不暴力、不破壞、不堵路、不縱火」，否則只會影響每一名市民。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員陳克勤認為，《禁止蒙面規例》成效需要一段時間觀察，現時評論是言之尚早。至於下星期三特首宣讀施政報告的安排，他表示，未有討論其他替代方案，希望能如常如期在立法會舉行。"},{"pid":"898afe473855fee87ca5e6ae9c334cb014ee0dbb","tid":1638351,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:36:14.000Z","msg":"一日黑警凌辱市民，一日都咪駛旨意會有民意逆轉割席<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/aNxWigT.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"3520c3bdea7a18e936210bdd6e6f2afd8d550774","tid":1638351,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:39:13.000Z","msg":"裝修邊間舖都有可能對唔準政權<br />\n裝修民建聯絕對冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dedf33d840ba6859e1ea7abaafb6d157a9e41b3","tid":1638351,"uid":267600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:44:58.000Z","msg":"與政府、黑警及你們一班人渣割蓆！"},{"pid":"6b59542e3471342a2e21b32acf625